{
  "stem": "13981.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 443.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I mentioned before, when I was seated near this witness Ohlendorf, an SS General Ohlendorf, when he mentioned in the trials, as a witness, that more than five million Jews met the final solution, or the final solution was applied to more than five million Jews.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a pretty-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] pretty hard-hitting moment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When did I what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to look it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went by train to Bremerhaven, and I took a boat there, and back to the United States.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was already discharged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I took my discharge.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a civilian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you were paid as a civilian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a civilian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they all want-- everybody wanted to know, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I showed my pictures to everybody who wanted to see them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I now take great delight, actual delight, in going to the schools, showing my documentary, which, for the schools, has been edited a little bit, to make it shorter, to make it fit into the time frame, and also to leave out some of the irrelevant talks that take place in there.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it gives me a great satisfaction to teach today's generation that these things are not inventions, that they actually happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when you show this picture, especially when the crowd is pretty harsh and awful, sudden this picture appears with a woman with her breast cut off, oh!",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The whole crowd.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, as long as their time permits.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have no time limit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some are pretty relevant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Other ones are childish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they ask me much how did you get these pictures?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What are your personal feelings about it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other ones are a little bit more philosophical.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
